Welcome to South Fork Village Apartment Homes.   We are located on the South Fork River and are minutes away from downtown Belmont, Cramerton, and Charlotte.  We are also close to Goat Island, Daniel Stowe Botanical Garden, and the U.S. National Whitewater Center.<br>
<br>
We offer spacious 1, 2, and 3-bedroom open floor plans with optional sunroom or patio.  These apartment homes feature fully equipped kitchens with granite countertops, over-sized closets, and 9-foot ceilings with crown molding.<br>
<br>
Our community has breathtaking river views, outdoor grilling areas, and access to the Carolina Thread Trail.  Be sure to also check out our zero-entry saltwater swimming pool with sundeck and 24-hour gym located at the club house.  You can also take it easy by visiting our coffee bar or on-site retail shops.<br>
<br>
Come visit your new apartment home at South Fork Village!  Call to schedule a tour today.
